OL,3,C'I want to win trophies': Lioness
OL,4,CGeorgia Stanway confirms move to
OL,5,CArsenal
OL,7,FEngland midfielder Georgia Stanway has
OL,8,Fjoined Arsenal on a permanent deal,
OL,9,Fthe Women's Super League club have
OL,10,Fannounced.
OL,12,FThe 27-year-old left Bayern Munich at
OL,13,Fthe end of the season and spent four
OL,14,Fyears with the Frauen-Bundesliga side,
OL,15,Fwinning eight trophies and featuring
OL,16,F128 times.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
