OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1783689573
OL,3,C'I want to win trophies': Lioness
OL,4,CGeorgia Stanway confirms move to
OL,5,CArsenal
OL,7,FStanway began her career with
OL,8,FBlackburn before joining WSL side
OL,9,FManchester City in summer 2015, where
OL,10,Fshe made 186 appearances and scored 67
OL,11,Fgoals in seven seasons, lifting one
OL,12,FWSL crown, three FA Cups and three
OL,13,FLeague Cups.
OL,15,FOn the international stage, the
OL,16,Fmidfielder has been capped 93 times
OL,17,Ffor England and was involved in both
OL,18,Fof the Lionesses' European
OL,19,FChampionship wins in 2022 and 2025.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
