PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1783689573
OL,3,C'I want to win trophies': Lioness
OL,4,CGeorgia Stanway confirms move to
OL,5,CArsenal
OL,7,FSpeaking about her move to north
OL,8,FLondon, Stanway said: "It's an
OL,9,Funbelievable feeling and I'm so proud
OL,10,Fto be joining Arsenal.
OL,12,F"This is a massive club that is
OL,13,Fdriving the women's game forward to
OL,14,Fnew levels and I want to be a part of
OL,15,Fit. I want to win trophies and grow as
OL,16,Fa player, and this is the right place
OL,17,Fto do that with the backing of an
OL,18,Fincredible fanbase."
