OL,3,C'I want to win trophies': Lioness
OL,4,CGeorgia Stanway confirms move to
OL,5,CArsenal
OL,7,FLast season Arsenal finished second in
OL,8,Fthe WSL standings, four points behind
OL,9,Fwinners Manchester City, and reached
OL,10,Fthe semi-finals of the Women's
OL,11,FChampions League.
OL,13,FGunners boss Renee Slegers said:
OL,14,F"Georgia is a brilliant midfielder and
OL,15,Fwe're thrilled that she is an Arsenal
OL,16,Fplayer.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
