PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1783689573
OL,3,C'I want to win trophies': Lioness
OL,4,CGeorgia Stanway confirms move to
OL,5,CArsenal
OL,7,F"She will add a new dimension to our
OL,8,Fmidfield, bringing experience and
OL,9,Fadding to our winning mentality. We
OL,10,Flook forward to getting down to work
OL,11,Fin pre-season ahead of a big campaign
OL,12,Fahead."
OL,14,FDirector of Women's Football Clare
OL,15,FWheatley added: "We're delighted to
OL,16,Fbring Georgia to Arsenal. Georgia is
OL,17,Famong the best midfielders in the
OL,18,Fworld with a proven track record of
OL,19,Fsuccess at club and international
OL,20,Flevel.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@GO]wD@QOU
