OL,3,C'I want to win trophies': Lioness
OL,4,CGeorgia Stanway confirms move to
OL,5,CArsenal
OL,7,F"She brings strong leadership,
OL,8,Fcharacter and competitiveness and I
OL,9,Fknow our supporters will enjoy
OL,10,Fwatching her play in red and white."
